Welcome

The Wilsons-1960

Welcome to the Wilson-Maynard Genealogy Web Site. Our family has a rich history, with Wilson ancestors coming to America in 1620, while the Maynards arrived ten years later.

Much of this information was assembled by Dr. Robert S. Wilson, who spent years researching our family history.

Information on us living folks is blocked for privacy. If you're a family member, please register for a log-in by clicking here.

We hope you enjoy a look back in our family's history. Features
